# Listae stack

- **App:** Next.js App Router + TypeScript (single repo). No separate Nest/Express API.
- **ORM/DB:** Drizzle + SQLite locally; schema must stay Postgres-portable.
- **Auth:** Auth.js magic link (email). No password auth in v1.
- **Cache:** DB-backed `SearchCacheStore`; Redis adapter later only — do not add Redis dependency in v1.
- **Deploy:** local-first until the owner requests hosting (ADR 006).
- **Not in v1:** MongoDB, social graph, long reviews, NestJS.

